Introduction

TWS is a six-member South Korean boy group formed by Pledis Entertainment. They debuted on January 22, 2024, with the mini album "Sparkling Blue." The group's name stands for "Twenty-Four Seven With Us," reflecting their official motto: "Twenty-Four Seven With Us! Hello, we are TWS!"

On November 7, 2023, Pledis Entertainment announced its first boy group in nine years since SEVENTEEN's debut. The group's official social media accounts launched on December 20, 2023, followed by confirmation of their debut schedule on December 27, 2023. Ahead of their official debut, TWS pre-released the single "Oh Mymy : 7s" on January 2, 2024.
